'''Docking Bay 3733''' was a spacecraft [[Hangar/Legends|docking bay]] attached to the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] by [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]]. It was part of [[Eastport/Legends|Eastport's]] [[Gate 3700]]. Its lighting was lit by pressing a [[wall-mounted illuminator bar]].

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] left the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] there, having leased the bay out under the assumed name "Vykk Draygo."

==Appearances==
*''[[The New Jedi Order: Vector Prime]]'' {{1st}}
